Class UnitType

Object
UnitType
public class UnitType
extends Object
This class provides a collection of all the unit types in the game. The information in valid for AoT, but not necessarily for AoM.
Author:
Mythic_Freak - mythic.freak[a]gmail.com
Note
Each unit also has its own unit type, those types are omitted., In scripts, the names of the variables here are prefixed with "cUnitType".
